commentPostTextItems.html: New Zealand win this match by 21 runs and seals the series by 3-0 with two more matches to go. West Indies started well their innings with Gayle and Morton going after every bowler. Then Fleming made a excellent move to bring his ace bowler Vettori who broke Morton and Sarwan partnership. The wicket are fell regular intervals, Bradshaw showed his batting skills during the end. But it already too late for West Indies. Pick of the bowler is Daniel Vettori who gave away 40 runs and picked coupld of wicket of his 10 overs. Please don't forgot to join with us on March 1 for the 4th ODI between this two teams. Till then bye from us
